{"type": "article", "id": 29443, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-07-11T23:01:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26164, "name": "Northern Lighting"}, {"id": 29712, "name": "Lyon Béton"}, {"id": 30055, "name": "NECKTIE"}, {"id": 30056, "name": "Attico"}, {"id": 30057, "name": "Tonelli Design"}, {"id": 20219, "name": "Katia Tolstykh"}, {"id": 27184, "name": "Cristina Celestino"}, {"id": 30058, "name": "Malgorzata Blachnicka"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160711174046UJGNfYLqQ9RVgD4v.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h3>Hauteville by Henri Lavallard Boget &amp; Julie Legros</h3>\n<p>法国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.lyon-beton.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lyon Béton</a> 一向以制作混凝土家具见长，最近 Henri Lavallard Boget 和 Julie Legros 携手打造了名为 Hauteville 的座椅系列，设计原型来源于 Boget 在废弃建筑物中发现的一把 50 年代的座椅。这个系列正在不断开发当中，全部采用混凝土和钢筋制作而成。Hauteville 的最新迭代款是一把摇椅，采用了符合人体工程学的造型设计，豪放又不失优雅。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.lyon-beton.com/store/concrete-furniture/hauteville-rocking-chair/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 594.79 欧元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712004022oKsSXH0IRmPqwxeB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120040232uV8Jarsn9CLj0Ug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712004023Dqx87yIXoebnYgcQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712004024U0ilOzKobmxW9G3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.512225\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712004023REnWoMCxmPNulif1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.806846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120040240NqVjHldaB69E4on.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Octagono by Katia Tolstykh</h3>\n<p>来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"http://katiatolstykh.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Katia Tolstykh</a> 利用黄铜和大理石设计出了一款结合烛台与花器的多功能容器 <a href=\"http://katiatolstykh.com/Octagono\" rel=\"nofollow\">Octagono</a>。极简的八边形大理石容器顶部和底部均采用了黄铜作为点缀，保证了稳定性。上方两个黄铜部件可以自由旋转，提供了额外的展示空间，不仅能够同时放置三根蜡烛，也能加入花草作为装饰，满足不同的日常需要。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003954UYc05lIyfskd8Fvo.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.003344\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003952PxLgF17JOoDwi50T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003952Alsin7aq5BDwKrfQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.463000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003952nAXRadewW3s1CUSI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.522000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003953EIUb2rXjSs5HGvD4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003953xpRYdPnsVj8OovKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.976000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Tea Bag Holder Shirokuma by NECKTIE</h3>\n<p>等待茶叶泡开的时间有了白熊的陪伴不会再觉得无聊了。这个纯白的陶瓷杯盖由日本工作室 <a href=\"http://necktie.tokyo/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NECKTIE</a> 设计，全部在以制作陶器为名的长崎县波佐见町由当地工匠手工烧制，陶瓷的加工和涂装则在东京的工厂进行。杯盖上的白熊举着一根竿子，泡茶时将茶叶袋的提线穿过它就好像是白熊正坐在冰面上钓鱼一样。这个可爱的杯盖适用于直径在 8 到 10 厘米的杯子，这是它的<a href=\"http://necktie.onlinestores.jp/category/select/pid/8765\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 3000 日元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003924XoEPtanhGDKpMCcy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003924O5mKz8UXASLE3qhf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003925IpnDHq8stuaSb5TX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003925xMwCcArgi1VW3R0K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003925SJ4fWyph3FQMqXYZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003926bqNnkJDlzuy15wCW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Grow by Malgorzata Blachnicka</h3>\n<p>室内种植系统并不算新鲜，来自奥地利的 <a href=\"http://www.blachnicka.eu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Malgorzata Blachnicka</a> 希望打造一个小巧简单，像是普通厨房用品的工具，这个微型温室 <a href=\"http://www.blachnicka.eu/portfolio/grow/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Grow</a> 就是她专门为家庭用户设计的培育系统。这个容器由玻璃钟罩和底座组成，内部可以嵌入两组特殊的薄板，底座则设计了一个蓄水盘，玻璃罩按下之后清水就会在罩内喷洒。种植时需要将种籽放在薄板上，它们会被板上的纹路紧紧包裹，板上的纤维组织还能够模仿自然条件加快成长。通过配套的应用扫描薄板上的二维码，用户可以随时查看生长的情况和各项指标，而且还能设置自动灌溉的频率。通过这种智能的方式，只需要三天就能吃上豆苗。Grow 目前还处于原型阶段，未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120038490g7CGPXzvZs8Wf2S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635697\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003851pUnL3XY6mDuWNgBa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.295844\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003850pFM0IQsiw3Eq1bm8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.853301\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003850GNC9vcx76wysUh5Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.891198\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003850xgwzPLEXlON14sJW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120038497UTGEeCM3tpb9q0K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Opalina by Cristina Celestino</h3>\n<p>炎炎夏日，玻璃家具所特有的清爽感能够让人眼前一亮。意大利设计师 Cristina Celestino 领导的设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.designattico.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Attico</a> 最近就为玻璃家具制作商 <a href=\"http://www.tonellidesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tonelli Design</a> 设计了一套名为 <a href=\"http://www.tonellidesign.com/eng/progettisti_dett.php?ID=120\" rel=\"nofollow\">Opalina</a> 的家具系列。Celestino 在设计时借鉴了 opaline 的概念，这个词语在 19 世纪之前指的是乳白色，后来逐渐用它同时来指代物品的颜色和材质。通过各种厚重玻璃之间巧妙的组合，Opalina 系列完全靠玻璃自身进行支撑，几乎看不到外部组件构成的结合，展现出了玻璃特有的光滑和剔透感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120038358B0oqzyO4Cgw1Qdv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003835iVlvjLhE7gK2wCUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.076667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003835vTNakCGHBrixfMyj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003836qgjfzxwB0YGbZT36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003836PF03jXsLkz2VJd5p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003836RagbxeV17Kp6Xyz2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.208333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h3>Snowball by Northern Lighting</h3>\n<p>挪威设计公司 <a href=\"https://northernlighting.no/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Northern Lighting</a> 最近推出的 <a href=\"http://minimalissimo.com/snowball-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snowball</a> 灯可以被称为包豪斯灯具（Bauhaus lamp）的现代版本：细长的金属杆连接着顶部雪球似的圆形灯泡与打磨过的立方体金属底座，线条流畅而优美，贯彻了包豪斯风格所透露出的未来感。Snowball 分为落地灯和台灯两款，极简的造型适用于不同的室内环境。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003802jVHtiSwlJ9LN6skF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120037579yNvHOeKtYZVLcoz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003759HqQkJuyhGlbs7TwN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607120038014VlMI6uakvYTA2CE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003801CeQ6Gt5ZxAW4DnB3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712003804f23jFa5IQgbWNwEK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}